org.sql: SELECT queries.* FROM queries LEFT OUTER JOIN projects ON queries.project_id = projects.id WHERE queries.type IN ('ProjectQuery') AND (queries.project_id IS NULL OR projects.status <> 9) AND (queries.visibility <> 0 OR queries.user_id = 1) AND queries.project_id IS NULL ORDER BY queries.name ASC, queries.id ASC
